    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": 1,
      "title": "How to read this board",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Gateway proxy metrics\n\n`gateway_*` metrics emitted by **`python main.py`** on `:9101/metrics`. They measure **HTTP proxy + tunnel** behavior, not raw vLLM internals.\n\n- **TTFT** is observed for **both** `stream=true` (first SSE chunk) and `stream=false` (full response time) traffic, so this board stays populated whichever mode `crew.py` runs in.\n- **Labels:** `technique` = `X-Technique` header (e.g. `baseline`, `chunked-prefill`, `chunked-prefill+prefix-caching+large-batch`); `server_profile` = Modal backend profile (`standard` / `optimized` / `hardcore`).\n- **Streaming inter-chunk** panels stay empty until at least one `Accept: text/event-stream` request runs through."
      },
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"}
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Request rate (5m)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "reqps"}, "overrides": []},
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false}, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "value"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "sum(rate(gateway_requests_total[5m]))", "legendFormat": "total", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"}
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 15,
      "title": "p95 TTFT (5m, all techniques)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 4},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s"}, "overrides": []},
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false}, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "value"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(gateway_ttft_seconds_bucket[5m])))", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"}
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 16,
      "title": "p95 E2E (5m)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 4},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s"}, "overrides": []},
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false}, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "value"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(gateway_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"}
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 17,
      "title": "GPU spend (last 1h)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 4},
